xCellerator Basic
====================================================================
To do a basic installation: open the file basic-installer.nb in 
Mathemtica, and from the Mathematica menu bar select 
evaluation -> evaluation notebook
====================================================================

This Basic file release contains the minimal set of files needed to 
install and run xCellerator, including xlr8r.m, mathSBML, kMech, SSA,
and basic palettes. It does not contain any documentation or help files,
which can be downloaded separately from the software repository. 

